---
const rows = [
	{
		model: 'Brastemp BFS5NCR',
		price: 'R$ 1.XXX',
		rating: '4,7/5',
		bestFor: 'Custo-benefício e uso diário',
		slug: 'brastemp',
		offerUrl: 'https://example.com/afiliado/brastemp-bfs5ncr',
	},
	{
		model: 'Consul CFS5NAB',
		price: 'R$ 1.XXX',
		rating: '4,5/5',
		bestFor: 'Orçamento enxuto',
		slug: 'consul',
		offerUrl: 'https://example.com/afiliado/consul-cfs5nab',
	},
	{
		model: 'Electrolux 76USQ',
		price: 'R$ 2.XXX',
		rating: '4,6/5',
		bestFor: 'Acabamento e forno espaçoso',
		slug: 'electrolux',
		offerUrl: 'https://example.com/afiliado/electrolux-76usq',
	},
];
---

<section class="border-b border-white/10 bg-ink py-16 lg:py-20" aria-labelledby="compare-heading">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<h2 id="compare-heading" class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
			Tabela comparativa: melhores fogões 5 bocas
		</h2>
		<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/55">
			Os valores de exemplo servem para você trocar pelos preços atuais quando atualizar os links. A ideia é decidir rápido: preço, nota e
			“melhor para”. Se quiser critérios antes da tabela, leia o resumo em{' '}
			<a href="/melhor-fogao-5-bocas" class="font-semibold text-pop underline-offset-2 hover:underline">melhor fogão 5 bocas</a>.
		</p>
		<p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-sm font-medium text-white/70">
			👉 Compare rápido e veja qual compensa mais hoje:
		</p>
		<div class="mt-10 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl ring-1 ring-white/10">
			<table class="w-full min-w-[640px] border-collapse text-left text-sm">
				<thead>
					<tr class="border-b border-white/10 bg-brand-900/80">
						<th scope="col" class="px-4 py-4 font-display text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">
							Modelo
						</th>
						<th scope="col" class="px-4 py-4 font-display text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">
							Preço (ref.)
						</th>
						<th scope="col" class="px-4 py-4 font-display text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">
							Avaliação
						</th>
						<th scope="col" class="px-4 py-4 font-display text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">
							Melhor para
						</th>
						<th scope="col" class="px-4 py-4 font-display text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">
							Ação
						</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
					{
						rows.map((r, i) => (
							<tr class:list={[i % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-ink' : 'bg-brand-900/30', 'border-b border-white/5 last:border-0']}>
								<th scope="row" class="px-4 py-4 font-semibold text-white">
									{r.model}
								</th>
								<td class="px-4 py-4 text-white/70">{r.price}</td>
								<td class="px-4 py-4 text-pop">{r.rating}</td>
								<td class="px-4 py-4 text-white/65">{r.bestFor}</td>
								<td class="px-4 py-4">
									<a
										href={r.offerUrl}
										class="inline-flex min-h-[44px] items-center justify-center bg-pop px-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-ink transition hover:bg-accent-hover"
										rel="nofollow sponsored noopener"
									>
										🔥 Ver preço atualizado
									</a>
									<a
										href={`/review-fogao-5-bocas-${r.slug}`}
										class="mt-2 block text-xs font-semibold text-white/50 underline-offset-2 hover:text-pop hover:underline"
									>
										Ver avaliação completa
									</a>
								</td>
							</tr>
						))
					}
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</div>
		<p class="mt-6 text-xs text-white/40">
			Compare também com o guia{' '}
			<a href="/comparativo-fogao-4-vs-5-bocas" class="text-pop/90 underline-offset-2 hover:underline">
				fogão 4 vs 5 bocas
			</a>{' '}
			antes de comprar.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>
